
To use doSplitAndMerge_allInOnce.sh:

./doSplitAndMerge_allInOnce.sh <libOfFragsToMerge1> <libOfFragsToMerge2> ... <libOfFragsToMergeN>

NB: the use of SplitAndMerge causes the generation of more than
    hundreds of files even for small libraries. 
    It is suggested to run these tools in a dedicated folder after proper modification of the script

